      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 56 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 56 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>旅，小亨，旅貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Lu intimates that (in the condition which it denotes) there may be some little attainment and progress. If the stranger or traveller be firm and correct as he ought to be, there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
