      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 56 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 56 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：旅瑣瑣，斯其所取災。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows the stranger mean and meanly occupied. It is thus that he brings on himself (further) calamity.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
