      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 56 六二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 56 六二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二：旅即次，懷其資，得童僕貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, shows the stranger, occupying his lodging-house, carrying with him his means of livelihood, and provided with good and trusty servants.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
