      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 56 九三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 56 九三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三：旅焚其次，喪其童僕，貞厲。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, shows the stranger, burning his lodging-house, and having lost his servants. However firm and correct he (try to) be, he will be in peril.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
