      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：旅于處，得其資斧，我心不快。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows the traveller in a resting-place, having (also) the means of livelihood and the axe, (but still saying), 'I am not at ease in my mind.'</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
