      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 56 六五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五：射雉一矢亡，終以譽命。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth SIX, divided, shows its subject shooting a pheasant. He will lose his arrow, but in the end he will obtain praise and a (high) charge.</seg>
